<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>登录 - 学生信息管理系统</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="auth-page">
  <main class="auth-shell">
    <section class="auth-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Student Hub</p>
      <h1>学生信息管理系统</h1>
      <p class="auth-text">
        面向日常教务协同的轻量后台，集中维护学生档案、班级运行情况和筛选导出任务。
      </p>
      <div class="auth-points">
        <div>
          <strong>学生档案</strong>
          <span>支持基础资料、状态、宿舍和紧急联系人维护</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>班级面板</strong>
          <span>按班级查看容量、辅导员和在读人数</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>数据导出</strong>
          <span>按筛选条件快速导出当前结果，便于留档</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="auth-card-wrap">
      <div class="auth-card">
        <div class="auth-card-header">
          <h2>账号登录</h2>
          <p>使用管理员账号进入后台</p>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/login" method="POST" class="auth-form">
          <div>
            <label class="form-label" for="username">用户名</label>
            <input
              id="username"
              type="text"
              name="username"
              class="form-control form-control-lg"
              placeholder="请输入用户名"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="form-label" for="password">密码</label>
            <input
              id="password"
              type="password"
              name="password"
              class="form-control form-control-lg"
              placeholder="请输入密码"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg w-100">登录</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
